snippet: A medical aircraft carrying the second of two American aid workers infected with the deadly Ebola virus took off from Liberia en route for the United States on Tuesday, a Reuters witness said....

headline.print_headline: Flight Carrying Second U.S. Aid Worker With Ebola Leaves Liberia
headline.main: Flight Carrying Second U.S. Aid Worker With Ebola Leaves Liberia

lead_paragraph: A medical aircraft carrying the second of two American aid workers infected with the deadly Ebola virus took off from Liberia en route for the United States on Tuesday, a Reuters witness said.
